<br>
In a small forest clearing,he removed his soot colored trench and layed it across a nearby tree branch.He then gathered wood,and created a fire. He then gathered 4 medium sized grey stones,and placed then each 2 feet from the fire,creating a square around the fire. Stepping into the square,he then removed a small handful of black dust from his belt pouch,and sat indian style infront of the fire.<br>
<br>
Stareing into the flames of the fire,he spoke. &quot;Lord of Darkness,spread your voice and send forth the one whome I seek.&quot; Once those simple words were spoken,he blew the black dust from his hand into the fire.<br>
<br>
Once the black dust made contact with the fires flames,the flames sparked and roared high in the air,before once again settling,but now,the flames were black.<br>
<br>
Goruka smiled lightly to himself,knowing his own voice had been heared. He remains seated infront of the fire and waits.<br>
