But she found that Goruka and the 'gift' he presented was far to interesting and sounded to good to pass up,and she immediatly goes after him. &quot;Goruka,wait....&quot; She grabs his shoulder,and stops him,then stands infront of him. &quot;I'm interested in your offer. What do I have to do?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenvaria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>QueenVaria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://hometown.aol.com/variaavande/images/tsianina2.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 299<br> <font color=#993300>(2/22/02 1:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/variaavande/images/tsianinasm.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> Varia narrowed her eyes at Zelia. ~How naive are you?~ she asked angrily. ~Can't you see he's playing you? Why would he possibly come here to offer you something good? Why? What reason could he have to want to help you? Out of the goodness of his heart? HA! People don't do that around here anymore... everyone has their motives, and everyone has a price. What's yours going to be? Your soul? AGAIN?~ <p><html> <font face="Signet Roundhand ATT" size="+1"> Varia Angelina Avande </font> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uiizeliaii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>II Zelia II</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 85<br> <font color=#993300>(2/22/02 2:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/iizeliaii/images/zel-1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Naive...maybe</span><hr size=1> Zelia looks at Varia,and frowns.<br>
<br>
&quot;I dont know! Why would anyone want to help me? That should be your question,Varia Avande! Had it ever crossed your mind that maybe not all people are bad?&quot; At first she was upset,but she calms down. She steps away from Goruka and walks over to Varia.<br>
<br>
&quot;Var,I can sence evil,and trust me,I don't sence it on this man. His aura is so peaceful. He wants to help me,is that such a bad thing?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugorukathemystic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goruka the Mystic</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#993300>(2/22/02 2:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ....</span><hr size=1> He watched in silent amusement at the two arguing over him. However his facial expression was of saddness,as if he were upset that Varia did not trust him. Indeed,Varia was a smart one,he had been warned of her by his goddess,but he had his own powers to convince people,either with his own humanly charm,or with one of his mystical charms.<br>
<br>
He plucks a flower from the earth,and lightly smells its fragrance as he watched the two. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenvaria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>QueenVaria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://hometown.aol.com/variaavande/images/tsianina2.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 301<br> <font color=#993300>(2/22/02 2:15 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/variaavande/images/tsianinasm.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Naive...maybe</span><hr size=1> Var immediately felt awful. She took Zelia and kissed her gently, and whispered in her ear. ~I'm afraid,~ she said, trembling a bit. ~So many people are out to destroy us being together, I just can't accept some stranger claiming to be giving gifts freely...~ Her eyes teared up a bit, she felt completely awful for hurting Zelia's feelings. How insensitive could she possibly have been, saying those things?<br>
<br>
She wrapped her arms around Zelia and pulled her close to her, burying her head in her shoulder. ~Please, baby, just don't go into this blind... do some investigating first?~ <p><html> <font face="Signet Roundhand ATT" size="+1"> Varia Angelina Avande </font> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uiizeliaii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>II Zelia II</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 86<br> <font color=#993300>(2/22/02 2:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ...Ok</span><hr size=1> Zelia gently strokes Varias hair. &quot;I just want us to be happy. If he could take away what he said he could,it's possible for me to be normal.&quot; Kisses the top of Varias head.<br>
<br>
Zelia was more blind to this Goruka,than any person ever,it was surely the power he was using against her,and only the power of Zelias dark bloodline could give him such power,and Zelia was not figureing this out.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'll do some investigating.&quot; She assured Varia. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenvaria.showPublicProfile?language=EN>QueenVaria</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://hometown.aol.com/variaavande/images/tsianina2.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 302<br> <font color=#993300>(2/22/02 2:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hometown.aol.com/variaavande/images/tsianinasm.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...Ok</span><hr size=1> ~Thank you,~ Var whispered. She just couldn't help it, even though Goruka was right there watching, she kissed Zelia with the most loving and passionate embrace she could. She held her so tight against her that she thought she might not be able to breathe after a few seconds. ~I... I know that what he offers sounds wonderful, but Zelia... like I said before, everything comes with a price. And... and without your memories of the past, you wouldn't be the wonderful woman you are today. The wonderful woman that I fell in love with, and the wonderful woman that I will always love.~ <p><html> <font face="Signet Roundhand ATT" size="+1"> Varia Angelina Avande </font> </html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uiizeliaii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>II Zelia II</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 87<br> <font color=#993300>(2/22/02 2:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Awwwwishness</span><hr size=1> And she kissed Varia back,and held her close,lovingly.<br>
<br>
She pondered Varia's words for a long moment,before once again breaking silence.<br>
<br>
&quot;That...what you said,sounds right. Maybe it is a bad idea to forget my past,but that's the price i'll pay if he can take away the destroyer.&quot; She looks to Goruka.<br>
<br>
&quot;Tell me,can you truely rid my being of the destroyer? If so,I will permanantly forget all the death i've cause,all those poor souls I've damned?&quot; Though Varia could help Zelia over-come anything,the power that was at work was something strong,something Zelia couldn't fight at the moment,she was seriously seduced by this man who could offer her what he offers. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showMessageRange?topicID=7.topic&start=21&stop=28>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showPrevMessage?topicID=7.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showNextMessage?topicID=7.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.emailToFriend?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.threadControl?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.unsubscribe